              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron energy spectrum at sample position was",
                "measured by means of the foil activation technique.",
                "It may be divided into three components with the",
                "respective neutron fluxes",
                "          Energy range                Flux",
                "             (MeV)                    n/(cm2s)",
                "- thermal (10E-10 < E < 1.42E-7)   (9.4 +- 2.8)E+2",
                "- epithermal (1.42E-7 < E < 0.06)  (1.85 +- 0.09)E+6",
                "- fast(0.06 < E < 20)              (1.40 +- 0.05)E+8",
                " The integral neutron flux is      (1.42 +- 0.05)E+8"
              ]
            }
